---
title: Sweet Chilli Chicken Rice Bowl with Pickled Onion & Toasted Sesame Dressing
description: This nutty delight uses sesame seeds, peanuts and sweet chilli sauce to top a flavourful mix of veggies and sliced chicken breast for a crave-worthy dinner that's as pretty as a picture.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-chilli-chicken-rice-bowl-0f244e0c.jpg
